00:15:59.592 --> 00:16:01.550 align:middle line:84%
You're thinking the
language of Michael Hedges.

00:16:01.550 --> 00:16:03.490 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden, you know
where those cord progressions

00:16:03.490 --> 00:16:04.290 align:middle line:90%
